Compilation and Installation:
--------------------------------

The simplest way to compile this package is:

Type `make' to build the executable (bacnet4linux).

$ make clean all

Run the package to get the optional command line parameters:
$ ./bacnet4linux ?

Run the package with your parameters:

$ ./bacnet4linux -d123

